{"tid":716920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區諾軒: 香 港 風 調 雨 順 , 料 七 一 遊 行 人 數 減","createTime":"2018-06-25T16:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T09:35:11.000Z","uid":49388,"like":3,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4e8ee32e5ffc27537255e5d29f1de357dac40db3","tid":716920,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/au-696x392.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Fau-696x392.jpg&h=0f040c98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n區諾軒(Instagram圖)<br />\n公眾集會及遊行上訴委員會就七一遊行起點問題展開上訴聆訊。本身是立法會議員的民陣副召集人區諾軒表示，現時是民主運動低潮，香港「風調雨順」下，相信參與遊行的人數較往年少，強調實際民情難以估計。<br />\n<br />\n民陣爭取東角道起步<br />\n民陣一方建議在銅鑼灣東角道或摩頓台巴士總站出發，並估計起步時只有3000人。區諾軒解釋，越來越多人改為在中途加入，相信以有關地點作為起點，已足以應付。他在回應委員會主席彭鍵基提問時，表示遊行舉辦多年，不少市民一家大小到場，主辦方有很大責任要確保安全，「公民抗命」並非主辦方希望做的事。對此，彭鍵基表示「這樣我就放心」。"},{"pid":"4b70e43e5923afe513b602db3a3efaf56c58dc6d","tid":716920,"uid":35815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:30:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dddfbab39eb255d1b6a3edcae58465636b25c82d","tid":716920,"uid":61278,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:33:22.000Z","msg":"又係呢個唔開會去日本既人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac0c62d7b657fcd4f8cf13e8fb6b66adb23f0e0","tid":716920,"uid":31841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:55:34.000Z","msg":"去日本旅行啦條撚樣"},{"pid":"e65e81ad36821f46ba9c116bd5fefde018f931e8","tid":716920,"uid":57566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T17:21:35.000Z","msg":"係啊，真係好適合調理農務啊"},{"pid":"3550dad40e3118ffed1de3fea72b362039aaa1eb","tid":716920,"uid":37808,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T17:26:28.000Z","msg":"風調