ts/faces/dog/zzz.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">投呢班共養戲子既就更加係白癡！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0dbed91f21871df870e073524fffbb4178c76393","tid":716920,"uid":20815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:07:45.000Z","msg":"飯民真係好撚離地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人數減唔係風調雨順，係差到唔想理囉屌你老母"},{"pid":"f0cb05130d879d94334f7d142cc0d9ccc8e7f09f","tid":716920,"uid":93784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:25:24.000Z","msg":"泛民不嬲後知後覺<br />\n<br />\n人數減 唔係風調雨順 <br />\n<br />\n民怨係加深左好多 71都疏導唔到<br />\n<br />\n事情發展只會係走向極端 一係激進 一係沉默當中滅亡<br />\n<br />\n同埋本身泛民號召力減弱係有原因 自國教後 <br />\n<br />\n泛民堅持和理非 拒絕本土意識 堅守老人政治 議會表現過於無能<br />\n<br />\n71民陣遊行又一直錯重點 最應該團結港人既泛民自己又玩分化對立 <br />\n<br />\n人數少係正常啦"},{"pid":"51c6f7a76d03c8c05c9d22a1f38f170c1a6adb9c","tid":716920,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:57:28.000Z","msg":"知唔知大概幾多人參加遊行?"},{"pid":"e698780ed7b124523cdbb032d8ff7f4f6cfbbb70","tid":716920,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:58:36.000Z","msg":"邊撚個呀你<br />\n企開D啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"9e42778f07c4159bea914fffda6103b001227aef","tid":716920,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T09:00:48.000Z","msg":"係因為你班仆街民主派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1972e2fcf4bf69abe29b0a3db7d0cc630f5e22c2","tid":716920,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T09:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3c1d33c47adaea9